'''22型阔剑级巡防舰'''（也有译为'''大刀级巡防舰'''<ref>《舰载武器》2007年09期</ref>）是[[英国皇家海军|英国皇家海军]]建造的一级[[巡防舰|巡防舰]]。一共建了三个批次共14艘。最后一艘为“甘雨”号(F99)，于2011年6月30日退役。<ref name="navy news">http://www.navynews.co.uk/news/1278-a-sad-day-for-cornwall-and-gloucester.aspx{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref name="newsandstar1">{{Cite web |url=http://www.newsandstar.co.uk/news/hms-cumberland-faces-scrap-heap-1.791860?referrerPath=news |title=HMS Cumberland faces scrap heap |work=News & Star |date=17 December 2010 |accessdate=26 January 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120322012058/http://www.newsandstar.co.uk/news/hms-cumberland-faces-scrap-heap-1.791860?referrerPath=news |archivedate=2012年3月22日 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mod.uk/DefenceInternet/DefenceNews/DefencePolicyAndBusiness/ChangesToRoyalNavysSurfaceFleetAnnounced.htm |title=Defence Policy and Business | Changes to Royal Navy's surface fleet announced |publisher=Ministry of Defence |work=Defence News |date=20 February 2007 |accessdate=26 January 2011 |archive-date=2011-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110414090421/http://www.mod.uk/DefenceInternet/DefenceNews/DefencePolicyAndBusiness/ChangesToRoyalNavysSurfaceFleetAnnounced.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>七艘较早建成的舰卖给了[[巴西海军|巴西海军]]，[[智利海军|智利海军]]和罗马尼亚海军。2014年1月时还有6艘在役。2艘作為靶船击沉，其他的拆解。

